
Welcome to the MC Framework! 

FEATURES CHANGES
----------------

* 2010-12-09, MC_Proc, process control wrapper for proc_* functions

* 2010-12-09, MC_Cacti_ScriptServer, use a common Cacti Script Server plugin for sever
  datasources

* MC_Cache_Time, a time window caching library.

* MC_Image, a limited image editor.  As of this writing it can resize,
  rotate, and copy images between formats 

IMPORTANT CHANGES
-----------------

* 

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
-------------------

MC Framework requires PHP 5.2.4 or later.

Zend Framework 1.97 or later. (optional, but required for some features)

INSTALLATION
------------

Please see INSTALL.txt.

